'''''Kwaku Ananse'''''  ni film ngufi ya 2013 iyobowe na Akosua Adoma Owusu<ref>Akosua Adoma Owusu</ref> . Filime ngufi ikomatanya ibintu byigice cya autobiographical hamwe numugani wa Kwaku Ananse, umunyamayeri mu nkuru zo muri [[Afrika]] yuburengerazuba na Karayibe bigaragara nkigitagangurirwa numugabo<ref>Kwaku Ananse - The Criterion Channel <nowiki>https://www.criterionchannel.com</nowiki> › kwaku-ananse</ref>. Umugani wa Kwaku Ananse uhujwe ninkuru y'umusore wo hanze witwa Nyan Koronhwea, witabiriye gushyingura se<ref>Kwaku Ananse | African Film Festival, Inc. <nowiki>https://africanfilmny.org</nowiki> › films › kwaku-ananse</ref>. Mu gihe cyo gushyingura, yasubiye mu ishyamba ashakisha se. Iyi filime yakinnye n'umucuranzi w'icyamamare Koo Nimo n'umukinnyi w'amafirime w'inararibonye Grace Omaboe<ref>2013 | Programme - Kwaku Ananse - | Berlinale | <nowiki>https://www.berlinale.de</nowiki> › archive › 02_programm_2013</ref> . 

Amashusho yanditswe hamwe n’umukinnyi wa firime wo muri Pakisitani n’umunyamerika akaba na rwiyemezamirimo Iram Parveen Bilal<ref>Kwaku Ananse | Kanopy <nowiki>https://www.kanopy.com</nowiki> › product › kwaku-ananse</ref> . Iyi nyandiko yandikiwe MaameYaa Boafo, umunyamerika wavukiye muri Pakisitani wavukiye muri [[Gana]], wahoze ari umukinnyi wa mbere nka Nyan Koronhwea<ref>2013 | Programme - Kwaku Ananse - | Berlinale | <nowiki>https://www.berlinale.de</nowiki> › archive › 02_programm_2013</ref>. Ariko, itsinda ryababyaye mumujyi wa New York amaherezo ryafashe umwanzuro wo gusubiramo imico mugihe cyabanjirije umusaruro hamwe na Jojo Abot, umuhanzi ukomoka muri [[Gana]]<ref>Akosua Adoma Owusu - Artforum International <nowiki>https://www.artforum.com</nowiki> › picks › akosua-adoma-ow...</ref>.  

== Inyandiko ==
Dushingiye ku migani ikungahaye yo muri [[Gana]], iyi filime ngufi y’ubumaji ihuza ibintu byanditswe mu buzima bwa Owusu n’imigenzo ya rubanda kugira ngo ivuga amateka y’umukobwa ukiri muto w’umunyamerika wagarutse muri [[Afurika]] y’iburengerazuba gushyingura se, ariko akavumbura umwirondoro we wihishe kabiri<ref>Interview: Akosua Adoma Owusu's 'Kwaku Ananse' at the ... <nowiki>https://www.indiewire.com</nowiki> › 2015/06 › interview-akos...</ref>.

Kwaku Ananse ni umugani gakondo wo muri [[Afrika]] y'uburengerazuba kubyerekeye ikiremwa kigizwe numuntu nigitagangurirwa, kimara imyaka ikusanya ubwenge bwose bwisi mumasafuriya y'imbaho. Mugihe agerageza guhisha inkono mugiti, ntashobora kubona uburyo bwo kuyishyira hejuru mumashami yacyo<ref>The Apagya Show Band - Kwaku Ananse | Various Artists <nowiki>https://soundwayrecords.bandcamp.com</nowiki> › track › the-a...</ref>. Iyo umuhungu we muto, Ntikuma amweretse inzira, Kwaku Ananse ararakara cyane, ajugunya inkono hasi. Iraturika kandi ubwenge burashira. Umuntu wese arihuta, yizeye gukiza ibyo ashoboye<ref>Kwaku Anansi: The only folklore character to travel out of ... <nowiki>https://face2faceafrica.com</nowiki> › article › kwaku-anansi-the...</ref>.

Nyan Koronhwea asubira kwa se Kwaku Ananse wavukiye muri [[Gana]] kumuhamba. Bari barabuze umubano hagati yabo kera. Yatandukanye ibyiyumvo by'ubuzima bwa se n'umuryango umwe muri [[Gana]] undi muri [[Amerika]]. Yarengewe n’ishyingurwa, asubira mu isi y’umwuka ashakisha Kwaku Ananse<ref>Interview with Akosua Adoma Owusu, director of Kwaku ... <nowiki>http://www.africine.org</nowiki> › entretien › interview-with-ako...</ref>.  

== Ibihembo ==
''Kwaku Ananse'' yatorewe kuba Golden Bear mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Berlin kandi yegukana igihembo cyiza cya Filime ngufi mu bihembo bya 9 bya Afurika Movie Academy Academy Awards .    Iyi filime kandi yakiriye abacamanza badasanzwe mu Ishyirahamwe Cinémas et Cultures d'Afrique 2015 i Angers, mu Bufaransa<ref>Kweku Anansi eni na ayefro - WorldStories <nowiki>https://worldstories.org.uk</nowiki> › reader › akan</ref>.
